FAIL_TO_PASS: when setOptionValue then value returned by opts
when option with required value specified then value as specified
when .version used with storeOptionsAsProperties() then version in opts
when boolean flag specified then value true
when boolean flag not specified then not in opts
when option with required value not specified then not in opts
when option with default value not specified then default value in opts
when storeOptionsAsProperties() then options stored on command
when storeOptionsAsProperties(true) then options stored on command
